questions.quote: She'll be fine. I gotta go to the hospital to see her tonight.
Good. Thank God. Good riddance. [pause] Oh listen, before you go, would you mind changing my diaper? HAA!!
Actually it was great. I met an Englishman, and we really, hit it off.
We can't eat here anymore, because he took a waitress out for a walk.
No, actually, we'd like to keep him here overnight for observation, just to be safe.
Hey you know what? I have access to one of the most deceitful, duplicitous, deceptive minds of our time. Who better to advise me?
I'm not letting him buy us a Cadillac. He hasn't got that kind of money.
Ha ha! We took it to you! You couldn't get it out of your zone all night. We were aggressive, we didn't let you penetrate!
